          "id": "x-swyx-2026-06-12-p1-s0",
          "text": "the #1 thing that is driving me to build my own vibecoding platform rn is that none of them - and i lov vercel, cloudflare, netlify etc - none of them really close the loop for you in terms of setting you on the right path with errors and pinging you when shit fails (shit always fails) there's way too much \"webmaster\" infra to setup for every single project and i just want to do it once and for all, instead i'm being asked to npx posthog wizard here and npx arize skills there and it all just needs to be swallowed up into One Thing.",
